<p><a href="https://global.oup.com/academic/product/statistical-thinking-from-scratch-9780198827634?cc=us&amp;lang=en&amp;">Statistical Thinking from Scratch</a>, Oxford University Press 2019</p>

<p>Code and supplementary material for the book are available on <a href="https://github.com/mdedge/stfs">GitHub</a></p>

<p>A review of the book can be found in <a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0169534719302794">Trends in Ecology and Evolution</a></p>

